ickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,1030],"id":"7059e0b8-4ce9-2fb3-cbaa-a72f9838a5f9","name":"Note: Abort — Malformed Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Segment Audience\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ ($json.score ?? 50) >= 50 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail) · ②→ Tag for Slow Nurture","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"88309a71-0b83-2ca0-1b03-cfc23030b952","name":"Note: Segment Audience"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail)\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Wait Before Step 2 · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,280],"id":"75eff3c2-ec0c-020d-79b4-27e87a56a709","name":"Note: Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag for Slow Nurture\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,880],"id":"dfa27d68-c86e-e1ea-7857-c35797393fb7","name":"Note: Tag for Slow Nurture"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Wait Before Step 2\n\nPauses 1 days — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Converted Already?","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"5d830734-91ed-62ba-a62f-58bf9631df49","name":"Note: Wait Before Step 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Converted Already?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.status }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail) · ②→ Mark Converted — Stop Drip","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"49d25c37-13b6-440e-ea8f-11a493f78b1e","name":"Note: Converted Already?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail)\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Update Drip Status · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"76ee5661-d7df-3428-2516-4ee8a96d8b2e","name":"Note: Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Mark Converted — Stop Drip\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"0e0cd0ee-24ce-1e0d-256c-ffb9f1802219","name":"Note: Mark Converted — Stop Drip"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Update Drip Status\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Summarize Run Stats · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"0dab043a-babf-b089-fcbc-262608769dcd","name":"Note: Update Drip Status"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"1ee1422e-6d76-7051-1f3c-a56d360c1f0f","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"cb4effdc-1f90-7deb-62f5-70ecd48ca9bd","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"94500201-d196-1f4a-d526-033d9a2fb02e","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,1540],"id":"02e348fb-5d43-ec48-49c2-2d0dd0965842","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,1540],"id":"879517d6-5d38-7a6e-d40a-4582f9656db6","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Qualify demo requests with HubSpot and Gmail hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** Lead Capture & Routing · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nQualify demo requests with HubSpot and Gmail hands-free. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual follow-ups is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Contact Form Submission → Required Fields Present? → Segment Audience → Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail) → Wait Before Step 2 → Converted Already? → Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail) → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to lead capture & routing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating follow-ups in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Scales without extra headcount\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"a31ca749-5405-f067-44f3-a8d0ccd51a7b","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"4e78a500-5216-381b-c9fe-68cd4634f5c9","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"0c7752a4-dcd9-72c1-23a5-7d6a3bcb5a3a","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your follow-ups process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"5867cf27-e542-a29a-1eac-b6d1e1b23eaa","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Contact Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Required Fields Present?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Required Fields Present?":{"main":[[{"node":"Segment Audience","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Abort — Malformed Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Segment Audience":{"main":[[{"node":"Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Tag for Slow Nurture","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Step 1 — Welcome (Gmail)":{"main":[[{"node":"Wait Before Step 2","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Wait Before Step 2":{"main":[[{"node":"Converted Already?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Converted Already?":{"main":[[{"node":"Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Mark Converted — Stop Drip","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Step 2 — Value Nudge (Gmail)":{"main":[[{"node":"Update Drip Status","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Update Drip Status":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag for Slow Nurture":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Mark Converted — Stop Drip":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"4f9d6b99-ad97-4020-a611-20755aae6b25","id":"FDX07963"}